text: It was really enjoyable. Lisa was easy to communicate with and there was a lot of space. The location was an easy 5-8 Uber ride to the Capital and all if the great restaurants downtown. We parked in the driveway and never moved the car. Didn't have to stress about traffic or being too far away from all our needs.
title: Eastside Bungalow SXSW/dwntwn
